---
import { ArrowRight } from "lucide-react";
---

<section class="bg-background py-10 sm:py-16 md:py-24 mt-8 sm:mt-16 md:mt-28">
  <div
    class="flex w-full flex-col items-center px-5 sm:px-10 md:flex-row md:items-center md:gap-10 lg:gap-14 md:px-16 lg:px-32 xl:px-64"
  >
    <!-- Imagen -->
    <img
      src="/images/IglesiaJCV.png"
      alt="Fachada de la iglesia Jesús Camino de Vida en Callao"
      class="w-full max-w-sm sm:max-w-md
        h-72 sm:h-96
        rounded-4xl sm:rounded-[25px]
        object-cover
        shadow-[0_12px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.14)]
        md:w-85 md:h-130 md:max-w-none md:shrink-0
        lg:w-125 lg:h-190
        xl:w-181.5 xl:h-274.5 xl:-mt-12"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />

    <!-- Contenido -->
    <div
      class="mt-8 sm:mt-10 w-full md:max-w-120 lg:max-w-140 xl:max-w-140 text-left"
    >
      <h2
        id="ven-y-conoce-title"
        class="font-heading text-[40px] sm:text-[52px] md:text-[52px] lg:text-[62px] xl:text-[69px] font-medium leading-[1.02] tracking-tight"
      >
        Ven y Conoce
      </h2>

      <p
        class="mt-3 sm:mt-4 md:mt-5 xl:mt-6 text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] md:text-[17px] lg:text-[19px] xl:text-[20px] leading-[1.35] sm:leading-[1.3] md:leading-tight xl:leading-[1.22] text-foreground/85"
      >
        Soñamos con un movimiento que no se queda, sino que va, que cruza
        fronteras y corazones para compartir el evangelio de Jesús. Un
        movimiento donde cada paso es una oportunidad para anunciar Su amor, y
        cada vida transformada se convierte en un testimonio vivo del poder de
        Dios.
      </p>

      <div
        class="mt-4 sm:mt-5 md:mt-5 xl:mt-7.5 space-y-1 text-[17px] sm:text-[18px] xl:text-[20px] leading-[1.3]"
      >
        <p><span class="font-bold">Domingos:</span> 10:00 a.m & 7:30 p.m</p>
        <p>
          <span class="font-bold">Lugar:</span> Parque Ricardo Palma 144 - Callao
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Botones -->
      <div
        class="mt-6 sm:mt-7 xl:mt-7.5 flex w-full flex-wrap sm:flex-nowrap items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 md:gap-5"
      >
        <a
          href="#"
          class="inline-flex h-11 md:h-12 min-w-36 sm:min-w-36.5 md:min-w-40 items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-primary px-5 md:px-8 text-[13px] sm:text-[14px] md:text-[15px] xl:text-xl font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.02em] text-primary-foreground shadow-[0_6px_12px_rgba(0,0,0,0.12)] transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90 md:normal-case md:tracking-normal md:shadow-none whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          ¿Eres Nuevo?
        </a>

        <a
          href="#"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 border-b-2 border-black pb-1 text-[12px] sm:text-[13px] md:text-[14px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.01em] text-foreground transition-all duration-200 hover:rounded-2xl hover:border-transparent hover:bg-black hover:px-5 hover:py-3 hover:text-white focus-visible:rounded-2xl focus-visible:border-transparent focus-visible:bg-black focus-visible:px-6 focus-visible:py-3 focus-visible:text-white md:font-normal md:normal-case md:tracking-normal whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          Conoce mas sobre nosotros
          <ArrowRight />
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
